originally put these pictures up on screen 24 hours.

161
00:11:23,653 --> 00:11:25,093
And anytime you looked at your screen,

162
00:11:25,433 --> 00:11:27,054
it was the same time of day in the picture

163
00:11:27,114 --> 00:11:29,034
that it was outside your actual windows.

164
00:11:30,455 --> 00:11:32,775
