00:13:21,223 --> 00:13:23,924
and we'll just get rid of those hills and all those trees,

194
00:13:24,024 --> 00:13:26,765
and now we're up in the stratosphere looking down at clouds.

195
00:13:27,705 --> 00:13:29,105
I'm going to load another palette here.

