214
00:15:00,546 --> 00:15:04,429
is because it was a mentally and creatively manageable space to work in,

215
00:15:05,090 --> 00:15:10,494
which I'm not sure a lot of our other much more cinematographic and three-dimensional things are quite the same,

216
00:15:11,075 --> 00:15:15,398
and because it wasn't going to evolve so quickly that as soon as you began to figure out what was going on,

217
00:15:15,458 --> 00:15:17,200
everything had changed and you had to start over.

