00:54:14,737 --> 00:54:17,779
one of the colors with the pattern,

829
00:54:17,819 --> 00:54:19,220
the cycling pattern you just made,

830
00:54:19,780 --> 00:54:21,861
and then you move it over slightly,

831
00:54:22,202 --> 00:54:23,542
